## 4) “The Code of Love” / heart canvas card page

### Main purpose

This is a **romantic love-letter style interactive page** with typed text, animated heart canvas, elapsed-time counter logic, autoplay audio, and a downloadable image button.

### Page setup

* Page title: **card**
* Loads:

  * Font Awesome
  * `default.css`
  * `jquery.js`
  * `garden.js`
  * `functions.js`
* Custom font face:

  * `digit` from `digital-7_mono.ttf`

### Audio feature

* Autoplay audio on page load
* Music source:

  * `goodby.mp3`

### Main layout

* Main wrapper:

  * `#mainDiv`
* Main content split into two visual areas:

  * left/code message area
  * right heart/canvas visual area

### Love-letter / code-style text section

The left section shows a stylized text block that looks like code/comments:

* “THE CODE OF LOVE”
* “Hey Saiba !”
* “Do you remember the day we first met?”
* “Since that day a spark begun;”
* “Your everything got imprinted in my heart;”
* “Journey from Infatuation to Love;”
* “Saiba, I will love you forever;”
* more personal closing lines

### Typewriter effect

* The code/message area uses:

  * `$("#code").typewriter();`
* So the text is revealed with a **typewriter animation**

### Heart download feature

* A heart icon button exists inside `#heartspan`
* Clicking it runs `downloadImage()`
* It triggers download of:

  * `Screenshot 2025-06-23 9.11.33 PM.png`
* Download filename is set as:

  * `filename.jpg`

### Heart/canvas visual section

* Right side contains:

  * `#loveHeart`
  * canvas with id `garden`
* This strongly indicates an animated heart/garden drawing effect handled by external scripts

### Love message display

Inside the heart area:

* name display:

  * **MISS SAIBA ARSHAD**
* main message:

  * **I LOVE YOU SO MUCH**
* signature:

  * **- STUPID**

### Relationship timer / elapsed time feature

* A `Date` object named `together` is initialized to:

  * September 5, 2016 at 16:30:00
* `timeElapse(together)` is called every 500 ms
* This means the page likely shows a **live relationship/love duration counter**

### Heart animation timing

* `startHeartAnimation()` is triggered after 5 seconds
* This suggests delayed heart bloom/particle animation after the intro begins

### Browser support fallback

* Checks whether canvas is supported
* If canvas is unsupported:

  * shows error message
  * hides code block
  * stops execution
* So it has basic compatibility fallback behavior

### Layout behavior

* `adjustCodePosition()` is called
* Suggests responsive/recalculated placement of the code block relative to heart animation

### Visual/interaction style

* Romantic “programmer love letter” concept
* Code/comment-themed text styling
* Animated heart visual
* Timed love counter
* Music + download action
* Combination of emotional message and interactive canvas art

### Summary of major features

This page includes:

* autoplay background audio
* typewriter love letter
* animated heart canvas area
* live elapsed-time love counter logic
* heart button for image download
* personalized romantic message display
* canvas fallback handling

